Rules of the game are :

1. You will be given 15 questions.
2. Every question has one correct answer.
3. You have 3 lifelines- 50-50, Phone a friend, Audience Poll. 
4. You can use all these lifelines only once.
5. Press 5 to use these lifelines.
6. You can quit whenever you want by pressing 0.
7. Prize money of Rs.1000 will be awarded for first 3 correct answers.
8. Prize money will keep on increasing to Rs.10000 per answer.
9. You cannot quit once you've used all the lifelines.
10. Enjoy the game.